Hello everyone,
Here I am posting because since July 1st I have had a bad trip on LSD,
I must say that before this bad trip I used to hit 20 nails a day and I used to do some work every two months with a lot of heavy drugs (Taz, coc, LSD, and the rest)...For 3 years,
Now I will tell you how it passed.
A good work awaits you
We had planned with 3 colleagues to take 10g of speed, 1g of MDMA and 2 vials of LSD.
Have a good Friday evening
We consumed 5 grams of speed plus all the day,
Saturday morning after a white night I go to work just in the morning from 9h to 12h in the afternoon,
We have not continued,
I continue to work on my side, tapping shells and tapping fast.
In the afternoon, evening arrives and two more colleagues join us. We had decided to take LSD on the beach (Personally, I was not reassured).
A colleague held the glass with a drop from the LSD vial for me.
I hesitated at first, then after I told myself, "Go ahead," I took it (something I shouldn't have).
The evening continues normally and the two other so-called colleagues had decided to make us work overtime excessively on our colleagues....
On this famous beach there were people and one of the two colleagues said, "There's no one looking for trouble, we're going to beat it up ..."
I think the product should go down because I couldn't fight like him.
so eventually I forced myself to resist the product,
